AFRICAN HORSE SICKNESS IN NAMIBIA
(Date of previous outbreak of African horse sickness in Namibia reported to
the OIE: July 2001).
Extract from the monthly report of Namibia for December 2002, received from
Dr John J.H. Shaw, Director of Veterinary Services, Ministry of
Agriculture, Water and Rural Development, Windhoek:
Location Otjimbingwe Suid No. 164 (22 deg 22 min S - 16 deg 8 min E) SV Omaruru
No. of outbreaks in December 2002: 1
